(19) What is CORS ?
Ans:-CORS stands for Cross Origin Resourse Sharing it is set of rules that web browsers follow to decide if a 
     website from one domain is allowed to make requests to another domain.

(20) What is S3 Inventory ?
Ans:- S3 inventory is like report card for Amazon S3 storage. it tells details about the files in your storage
      like how big they are.

